{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T00:29:42.494Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Anthropic Console's Test Case Generation"},{"type":"text","text":" feature allows you to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"automatically create test cases using Claude"},{"type":"text","text":" to evaluate your prompts against real-world inputs. This eliminates the need for manual management across spreadsheets or code."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The key benefit:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"The Evaluate tab enables you to automatically create test cases to evaluate your prompt against real-world inputs.\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Test Case Generation Does"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Core Capabilities"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The new Evaluate tab enables you to automatically create test cases to evaluate your prompt against real-world inputs. Modify your test cases as needed, then run all of them in one click.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Auto-generate test cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Claude creates test cases for you\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Modify test cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Adjust after generation\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Run all tests in one click"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Execute entire test suite\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Compare outputs side by side"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” View multiple prompt versions\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5-point scale grading"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Subject matter experts grade responses"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How to Access Test Case Generation"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 1: Navigate to the Evaluate Tab"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"To get started with the Evaluation tool: Open the Claude Console and navigate to the prompt editor. After composing your prompt, look for the 'Evaluate' tab at the top of the screen.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Access steps:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. Open "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"console.anthropic.com/dashboard"},{"type":"text","text":"\n2. Navigate to prompt editor\n3. Click "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Evaluate\""},{"type":"text","text":" tab at top"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 2: Ensure Prompt Has Variables"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Ensure your prompt includes at least 1-2 dynamic variables using the double brace syntax: {{variable}}. This is required for creating eval test sets.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Required format:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyze this text: {{input_text}}\n\nInstructions:\n- Summarize the main points\n- Identify the tone\n- Extract key entities"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Variables must use:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"{{variable_name}}"},{"type":"text","text":" syntax"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 3: Create Test Cases (3 Options)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"When you access the Evaluation screen, you have several options to create test cases:\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Option 1: Manual Input"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Click the '+ Add Row' button at the bottom left to manually add a case.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. Click "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"+ Add Row"},{"type":"text","text":"\n2. Fill in variable values\n3. Add ideal answer (optional)\n4. Save"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Option 2: Auto-Generate with Claude"},{"type":"text","text":" вӯҗ"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Use the 'Generate Test Case' feature to have Claude automatically generate test cases for you.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. Click "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Generate Test Case\""},{"type":"text","text":"\n2. Claude generates "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"one row at a time"},{"type":"text","text":" per click\n3. Review and edit if needed\n4. Repeat to generate more"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Click \"Generate Test Case\" вҶ’\nClaude generates:\n{\n  \"input_text\": \"Our new product launched last week and exceeded all sales targets. We're thrilled with the customer feedback and revenue growth.\"\n}\n\nClick again вҶ’\nClaude generates:\n{\n  \"input_text\": \"The customer service team is overwhelmed. We've received 50 complaints in the last 3 days about slow response times and unresolved issues.\"\n}"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Option 3: Import from CSV"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Import test cases from a CSV file.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. Create CSV with test data\n2. Import into Console\n3. Map columns to variables"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How to Use the \"Generate Test Case\" Feature"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 1: Click \"Generate Test Case\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Click on 'Generate Test Case'. Claude will generate test cases for you, one row at a time for each time you click the button.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Click once вҶ’ Claude generates one test case"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Click again вҶ’ Claude generates another test case"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 2: Edit Generation Logic (Optional)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can also edit the test case generation logic by clicking on the arrow dropdown to the right of the 'Generate Test Case' button, then on 'Show generation logic' at the top of the Variables window that pops up.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How to edit generation logic:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. Click "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"arrow dropdown"},{"type":"text","text":" next to \"Generate Test Case\" button\n2. Click "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Show generation logic\""},{"type":"text","text":"\n3. Edit the logic in the Variables window\n4. Click "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Generate\""},{"type":"text","text":" to populate initial logic"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Fine-tune"},{"type":"text","text":" what test cases look like\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Customize"},{"type":"text","text":" for specific requirements\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Adjust"},{"type":"text","text":" Claude's understanding"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 3: Modify Test Cases"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Modify your test cases as needed, then run all of them in one click.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What you can modify:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Variable values"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Edit input text\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ideal answers"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Add expected output\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add more cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Generate additional test cases\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Delete cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Remove unwanted tests\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Edit logic"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Adjust generation parameters"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Evaluation Workflow"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Add Ideal Answers"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can add the 'ideal' answers and score the results.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Purpose:"},{"type":"text","text":" Expected output for each test case"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test Case:\nInput: {{review}} = \"This phone is amazing! Battery lasts all day.\"\n\nIdeal Answer:\n- Sentiment: Positive\n- Rating: 5/5\n- Key points: Battery life, Phone quality"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Run Tests on All Prompt Versions"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The Evaluate tab enables you to automatically create test cases to evaluate your prompt against real-world inputs.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Select prompt versions"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Choose which prompts to test\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Click \"Run all tests\""},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Execute entire test suite\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"View results"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” See outputs for each test case"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Compare Outputs Side by Side"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Compare the outputs of two or more prompts side by side.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Visualization:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test Case 1: \"This phone is amazing!\"\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\nв”Ӯ Prompt A (Original)                 в”Ӯ Prompt B (Improved)                 в”Ӯ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\nв”Ӯ Sentiment: Good                     в”Ӯ Sentiment: Positive                 в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ Rating: 4/5                         в”Ӯ Rating: 5/5                         в”Ӯ\nв”Ӯ Key points: Battery                 в”Ӯ Key points: Battery life            в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\nв”Ӯ Score: 3/5 (missing key details)    в”Ӯ Score: 5/5 (perfect match)          в”Ӯ\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Grade on 5-Point Scale"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"As you iterate on different versions of the prompt, your subject matter experts can compare responses and grade them on a 5-point scale.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Scoring guide:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5/5"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Perfect match with ideal answer\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4/5"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Very good, minor differences\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3/5"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Acceptable, but noticeable gaps\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2/5"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Poor, missing key elements\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1/5"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Failed completely"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5. Review Scores and Iterate"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can add the 'ideal' answers and score the results, which could be used to collaborate between teams, or even score future prompt versions automatically with an LLM.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Iteration process:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Review scores"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” See which prompt performed better\n2. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Identify improvements"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Note what worked\n3. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Modify prompt"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Apply improvements\n4. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Re-run tests"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Test new version\n5. "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Repeat"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Continue until satisfied"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Automatic Test Case Generation Features"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Smart Variable Understanding"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Users can manually add or import test cases from a CSV or auto-generate them using Claude. The Evaluate feature in the Console allows for direct testing of prompts against a range of real-world inputs.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude understands:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Variable types"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Text, number, boolean, etc.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Context requirements"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” What kind of input is needed\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Domain specifics"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Industry or use case requirements"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Diverse Test Coverage"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Create and manage extensive test suites in the Console. You can manually input test cases, import them in bulk, or ask Claude to auto-generate test cases for you with the 'Generate Test Case' feature.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude generates:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Happy path cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Typical, expected inputs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Edge cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Unusual but valid inputs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Error cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Invalid or problematic inputs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Boundary cases"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Very long, very short, empty"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generation Logic Customization"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Edit the test case generation logic by clicking on the arrow dropdown... You may have to click 'Generate' on the top right of this window to populate initial generation logic.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What you can customize:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Input diversity"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” How varied test cases should be\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Domain focus"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Specific industries or topics\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complexity"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Simple vs. complex inputs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Edge case frequency"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” How many edge cases to generate"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Examples"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 1: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Customer Feedback Summarization"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Summarize this customer feedback: {{feedback_text}}\n\nInstructions:\n- Extract key points\n- Identify sentiment\n- Rate satisfaction (1-5)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Auto-generated test cases:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test Case 1 (Happy Path):\n{\n  \"feedback_text\": \"The new feature is amazing! It saved me 10 hours this week and the interface is so intuitive. I love how easy it is to use.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 2 (Edge Case - Negative):\n{\n  \"feedback_text\": \"The tool crashed 3 times today. I lost all my work and had to re-enter everything. This is unacceptable.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 3 (Edge Case - Mixed):\n{\n  \"feedback_text\": \"The core functionality is great, but the mobile app is buggy and slow. I can't use it on my phone.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 4 (Boundary Case - Very Short):\n{\n  \"feedback_text\": \"Good.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 5 (Boundary Case - Very Long):\n{\n  \"feedback_text\": \"I've been using this product for 6 months and I have a lot to say. First, the onboarding was smooth and the team was responsive. However, after 3 months, the pricing increased by 30% which was frustrating. The features are solid but I wish there were more customization options. The documentation is helpful but outdated. Overall, I'm satisfied but there are definitely areas for improvement...\"\n}"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 2: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Product Review Classification"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classify this product review: {{review}}\n\nOutput format:\n- Category: [string]\n- Sentiment: [positive|negative|neutral]\n- Rating: [1-5]\n- Key points: [array]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Auto-generated test cases:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test Case 1:\n{\n  \"review\": \"This phone is amazing! Battery lasts all day and camera is crystal clear.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 2:\n{\n  \"review\": \"Terrible experience. The screen broke after 2 days and customer service was unhelpful.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 3:\n{\n  \"review\": \"It's okay. Does what it's supposed to do, nothing special.\"\n}\n\nTest Case 4:\n{\n  \"review\": \"Great value for the price.\"\n}"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Eliminates Manual Work"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The Evaluate feature in the Console allows for direct testing of prompts against a range of real-world inputs, eliminating the need for manual management across spreadsheets or code.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Before:"},{"type":"text","text":" Create test cases in Excel, run manually, track in spreadsheets "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"After:"},{"type":"text","text":" Auto-generate, run in one click, track in Console"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Speeds Up Iteration"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Generate, test, and evaluate prompts in Anthropic's Developer Console with Claude 3.5 Sonnet. Prompt quality significantly impacts the results of your AI applications.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Process becomes:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n1. Generate test case вҶ’ Click (1 second)\n2. Run all tests вҶ’ Click (10-30 seconds)\n3. Compare outputs вҶ’ See side-by-side view\n4. Grade вҶ’ 5-point scale\n5. Iterate вҶ’ Modify prompt"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Enables Collaboration"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can add the 'ideal' answers and score the results, which could be used to collaborate between teams.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Subject matter experts"},{"type":"text","text":" can grade responses\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Teams can share"},{"type":"text","text":" test cases and scores\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multiple reviewers"},{"type":"text","text":" can compare perspectives"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Improves Prompt Quality"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"These features streamline prompt development and improve model performance.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Results:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"30% accuracy boost"},{"type":"text","text":" in classification tests\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"100% word count adherence"},{"type":"text","text":" in summary tests"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test Suite Management"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Create Extensive Test Suites"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Create and manage extensive test suites in the Console.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Capabilities:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Manual input"},{"type":"text","text":" вҖ” Add cases one by one\n- "},{"type